The Atlantis-simulated fishery length composition for the mskeyrun project

Source: R/simFisheryLencomp.r
simFisheryLencomp.Rd

Simulated fishery length composition data from Atlantis model as sampled by atlantisom

simFisheryLencomp

Format

A data frame

ModSim

Atlantis model name and simulation id

year

year simulated survey conducted

Code

Atlantis model three letter code for functional group

Name

Atlantis model common name for functional group

fishery

simulated fishery name

lenbin

1 cm length bin, lower limit

variable

number at length (Natlen)

value

value of the variable

units

units of the variable
